    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A Stylish Collaboration: Key Features of the Rolling Links Collection",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The <em>Rolling Links</em> collection features an array of unisex apparel that perfectly balances technical performance and a laid-back, skate-inspired aesthetic. The range focuses on delivering relaxed yet athletic silhouettes in a versatile colour palette that includes greens, whites, blacks, and blues - colours synonymous with both the skate and golf worlds.</p><p>Key pieces in the collection include:</p><ul><li><strong>Long-sleeve polo with subtle vertical stripes</strong>: This polo offers a modern twist on a golf classic, with contrasting collars and subtle detailing to add a touch of skate culture flair.</li><li><strong>Nylon gilet with knit waist and collar</strong>: Functional yet stylish, the gilet provides warmth on cooler days on the course while maintaining a sleek, contemporary look.</li><li><strong>Mock-neck short-sleeve shirts</strong>: Designed for a casual, sporty feel, the mock-neck shirt is a nod to skate fashion, where relaxed fits and minimalist design dominate.</li><li><strong>Crewneck windshirt</strong>: This lightweight, versatile windshirt is ideal for both golf and everyday wear, embodying the easy-going style of skateboarders while offering protection against the elements.</li><li><strong>Chinos and shorts</strong>: Available in muted tones like grey and black, these bottoms are perfect for both the course and the streets, with subtle adidas three-stripe detailing along the hem.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
